item.description:
Summer was so much fun!  Now is the time for a 30 day Raw Food Challenge!!!  Are you up for it?  Max 25 enrolled.  Daily communication, once a week get together....end of the 30 celebration  .I know I am ready to be here for you!  Cost is $20

The official start day will be Sept 15.  We will meet the night before Fri 9/14 to answer any questions you might have.

 

Payments are thru Paypal, mail or in person.

If paying by paypal   kosrawadventures@gmail.com
